# Build outputs
**/obj/
**/bin/
**/packages/

# IDE files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.sln.docstates

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Runtime data
**/pids/
