# Dependency directories
**/node_modules/

# Optional npm cache directory
**/.npm

# Optional REPL history
**/.node_repl_history

# OS generated files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Docker files
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/.dockerignore

wwwroot/app/manifest/